  "title": "Bookstore Cashiers X 50 @ (North-East / West) | $2200 - $2300 per month | Immediate Hire!",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🌟 Join Our Team as a Bookstore Retail Cashier – Great Benefits and Competitive Pay! 🌟</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are on the lookout for <strong>enthusiastic, customer-focused individuals</strong> to join our team as <strong>Bookstore Retail Cashiers</strong>. If you have a passion for delivering exceptional service and love working in a fast-paced retail environment, we want to hear from you!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Position Available:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Retail Cashier</strong> – From <strong>$2,300/month</strong> </li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate the POS system to process purchases accurately</li>\n  <li>Assist with returns, exchanges, and ensuring customer satisfaction </li>\n  <li>Display merchandise, replenish stocks, assist in stock-taking, and receive orders </li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean, organized, and welcoming store environment </li>\n  <li>Identify and capitalize on sales opportunities to enhance customer experience </li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Work Schedule</strong>: 44 hours per week, 5-day work week (1 weekday off, 1 weekend off) </li>\n  <li><strong>Retail Hours</strong>: Required for store operating hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Block-Out Period</strong>: Nov/Dec peak period </li>\n  <li>A <strong>positive, customer-focused attitude</strong> and strong teamwork skills </li>\n  <li>Able to <strong>start at short notice</strong> </li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>A dynamic, team-oriented work environment </li>\n  <li>Full training provided to help you succeed in your role </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready to Apply?</strong><br>\nIf you’re passionate about delivering excellent service and eager to join our team, please send your resume in <strong>MS Word format</strong> to <strong>deborah@crew.sg</strong>, along with your availability, current salary, and last drawn salary.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We look forward to hearing from you! 😄</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Contact</strong>: 9186 0276<br>\nHo Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)<br>\nCrew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd<br>\nEA24C2435</p>",
